0486324","tid":1010681,"uid":53705,"like":158,"dislike":0,"score":158,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T08:18:43.000Z","msg":"千奇唔好比 大陸人睇到呢單新聞<br />\n<br />\n否則又會有成千上萬 大陸人來香港打疫苗"},{"pid":"54f908d743152bf7dc4e8156d1cb9f4a3ebe4314","tid":1010681,"uid":169071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T08:21:30.000Z","msg":"痴撚線國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd118f58f63b465a4462ac5ee27dfce7fdb86c95","tid":1010681,"uid":123738,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T08:22:00.000Z","msg":"支那狗驚閪！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一早成身都係啦"},{"pid":"4bef09ae2864eb70c963d7724c7b259b0e809f00","tid":1010681,"uid":202464,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T08:22:24.000Z","msg":"停止施打？<br />\n<br />\n咩中文黎？"},{"pid":"608e39a9dac3d92b5972d73994a8a31bcf1a069e","tid":1010681,"uid":190540,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T08:23:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e7170e40c15d239139d185d8d846b8fe60747d53","tid":1010681,"uid":190540,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T08:24:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c02ca3273c60407ed0e60c1517d2a1412d2399d","tid":1010681,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T08:25:40.000Z","msg":"有抗體冇抗原都會中招??<br />\n但佢由抽血到製藥搞咁耐仲有冇感染能力"},{"pid":"a67da1e53e3d9bdf38886d0d5ff17ccae7ce0250","tid":1010681,"uid":197640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T08:25:42.000Z","msg":"好奇想問，係啲原料出事定係個廠房有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b472d6eb405ee121e0d79e92bb85c658562ac7","tid":1010681,"uid":18844,"like":10,"dislike":10,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T08:36:22.000Z","msg":"報紙佬真係....<br />\n抗體還抗體, 抗原還抗原....<br />\n<br />\n免疫球蛋白 (疫苗)<br />\n免疫球蛋白 = 抗體 = antibodies (捐血清者的身體製造)<br />\n其實就係混合晒機乎所有可能性的抗體..<br />\n唔排除係捐血既人中左愛滋所有身體產生左HIV antibodies<br />\n<br />\n但佢收集完啲血清應該會做<br />\nlow/high pH virus inactivation<br />\n<br />\nHIV係pH 偏離左7.1之後都可以有效地被inactivate<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/public-health/services/laboratory-biosafety-biosecurity/pathogen-safety-data-sheets-risk-assessment/human-immunodeficiency-virus.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.canada.ca%2Fen%2Fpublic-health%2Fservices%2Flaboratory-biosafety-biosecurity%2Fpathogen-safety-data-sheets-risk-assessment%2Fhuman-immunodeficiency-virus.html&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTH8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=5ee3a885\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.canada.ca/en/public-health/services/laboratory-biosafety-biosecurity/pathogen-safety-data-sheets-risk-assessment/human-immunodeficiency-virus.html</a><br />\n或者升少少溫度都ok"},{"pid":"ec6c69528a750490b3d156e01b96e33f14dfb0a7","tid":1010681,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a67da1e53e3d9bdf38886d0d5ff17ccae7ce0250","tid":1010681,"uid":197640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T08:25:42.000Z","msg":"好奇想問，係啲原料出事定係個廠房有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T08:38:20.000Z","msg":"佢生產方法係搵人捐血清..<br />\n睇過少少, 應該係啲廠會養一班人居定時間去捐..<br />\n<br />\n疫苗專家陶黎納向《中國經營報》記者介紹，免疫球蛋白是人體血液中的抗體，靜脈注射人免疫球蛋白是利用從人體血液提取出的免疫球蛋白制備的免疫制劑，是一種廣譜抗病毒制劑，一般在臨床上用於治療免疫疾病，如川崎病等。免疫球蛋白與疫苗是不同的概念，疫苗可以產生免疫球蛋白，主動使人產生免疫力，廣譜和特異性的免疫球蛋白是被動免疫，在人體內有半衰期。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　據陶黎納介紹，目前還沒有發現過艾滋抗體陽性，血液制品仍有傳染性的情況，因此注射該批次免疫球蛋白的患者感染艾滋病的可能性不大。免疫球蛋白在生產過程中會對微生物體滅活，但仍保留生物蛋白質的活性。但即便對患者可能不會產生實質影響，這批次產品仍不該被生產出來，這次事件反映了生產廠家的質控出現了問題。<br />\n<br />\n　　陶黎納認為，理論上講，用於生產該批次免疫球蛋白的血液采集時就是攜帶艾滋病毒的，也就是說供血者感染了艾滋病。目前國內靜注人免疫球蛋白的生產模式是由生產廠家&ldquo;養&rdquo;一批固定人群，專門用來提供血液，這在醫學倫理上仍處於灰色地帶。對於已經注射該批次免疫球蛋白的患者，陶黎納建議按照接觸過艾滋暴露源的人群進行觀察。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.sina.com.cn/c/2019-02-06/doc-ihrfqzka3888731.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.com.cn%2Fc%2F2019-02-06%2Fdoc-ihrfqzka3888731.shtml&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTH8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=60ee24ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.sina.com.cn/c/2019-02-06/doc-ihrfqzka3888731.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"b40a9aac07ac5756d0f619c69a988b0393f09caf","tid":1010681,"uid":134226,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T08:43:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Contaminated_blood_scandal_in_the_United_Kingdom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FContaminated_blood_scandal_in_the_United_Kingdom&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTH8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=de5e4f8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Contaminated_blood_scandal_in_the_United_Kingdom</a><br />\n英國都發生過類似嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過係搵啲道友同囚犯賣血 之後用嚟整凝血劑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c006bdc1a010ffc6cb155155a95b418fc5435506","tid":1010681,"uid":62946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T08:54:26.000Z","msg":"全民齊打愛滋針<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99c4193225105700fc2a8f87d4105e44d0d87483","tid":1010681,"uid":80103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T09:04:03.000Z","msg":"恭喜哂啦"},{"pid":"e0c37777ea2ba3b04dd511b2bdf50a80c2ee846e","tid":1010681,"uid":182820,"like":22,"dislike":5,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"f83438d5263348a40a84ce9262bf828280486324","tid":1010681,"uid":53705,"like":158,"dislike":0,"score":158,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T08:18:43.000Z","msg":"千奇唔好比 大陸人睇到呢單新聞<br />\n<br />\n否則又會有成千上萬 大陸人來香港打疫苗"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T09:04:48.000Z","msg":"香港公立醫院冇得打免疫球蛋白，因為風險高，如果病人打左出事分分鐘俾人告。免疫球蛋白的原材料係人類既血液，大陸果陣有人去鄉村收血其中部份就係要黎做呢種針藥，由於人類可以有好多種唔同的疾病響身，而驗血都未必驗得晒出黎，所以用血液造的針藥其實好危險的。香港某部份藥房都有免疫球針藥賣，有些人會響香港買外國造的返大陸，不過由於係血製品，所以就算外國造都未必安全。大陸人通常響病人病到可能唔得既時候就會用免疫球蛋白針，有部份人打左後身體就會增強番對疾病的抵抗力，可以過到呢一關，就算唔得通常打左後都可以精神清醒番一段時間，有咩要交待都可以有時間講清楚。"},{"pid":"15c02bd65743bc596758173022046f9c8ab98ecb","tid":1010681,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T09:04:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0255d519d4e77cf68f47668f6d7cdfd57b15e6c9","tid":1010681,"uid":71071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T09:05:40.000Z","msg":"滅族不遠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f7fd24af0355afd6775a612596bad25f391df86","tid":1010681,"uid":160534,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T09:11:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z0cTKrN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ0cTKrN.png&h=c9d5976a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c769a21266a90b3c6953409b7a44c288c5b2bfdc","tid":1010681,"uid":86509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T09:16:28.000Z","msg":"中華人民共和國成立初，微生物學家湯飛凡帶領下的中央人民政府衛生部生物製品研究所（由中華民國中央防疫處改編而來），協助進行了國產化疫苗的研製生產；湯飛凡等專家建議，由衛生部在全國範圍內普遍種痘，之後由周恩來簽發《關於發動秋季種痘運動的指示》；中國大陸地區在1961年通過接種牛痘疫苗消滅了天花。但在建國後到改革開放前的這一時期，沒有明確的法規組織免疫接種。<br />\n<br />\n在政治波動中，預防免疫事業幾乎停滯。中國大陸自1978年開始，實施「國家免疫規劃」，具體是指按照國家或者省、自治區、直轄市確定的疫苗品種、免疫程序或者接種方案，在人群中有計劃地進行預防接種，以預防和控制特定傳染病的發生和流行。<br />\n<br />\n在改革開放之後，中國大陸也受到了國際上的廣泛援助，如從1979年開始，日本對華開發援助，即包括了針對傳染病防治的項目；而80～90年代，默克藥廠也向中國轉讓疫苗技術，在1989年達成與中國政府的技術轉讓許可，出讓了當時最先進的基因工程乙肝疫苗生產技術。加快了更多疫苗的國產化進程。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n勁樣衰要比自己大仇人救<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後攞咗技術都做唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be145123d36997e7ded7a7c4a8aae3430272b309","tid":1010681,"uid":22362,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T09:18:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sADvMG9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsADvMG9.png&h=b0f1dcc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全額退款<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a91a367244da72a2ba2cf7b6c2eb17d4dc30d946","tid":1010681,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T09:23:39.000Z","msg":"造謠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，樓主試下SD去大陸網。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0238327462176af5cbec07f67bed6e65806df81e","tid":1010681,"uid":110298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T09:27:03.000Z","msg":"愛滋針<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18933a92507ac5270388940c54a6adec7795f321","tid":1010681,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T09:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81de24bf79e6236179087242ec0ce6d9aca38c68","tid":1010681,"uid":205162,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f83438d5263348a40a84ce9262bf828280486324","tid":1010681,"uid":53705,"like":158,"dislike":0,"score":158,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T08:18:43.000Z","msg":"千奇唔好比 大陸人睇到呢單新聞<br />\n<br />\n否則又會有成千上萬 大陸人來香港打疫苗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T09:32:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啱聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a891eb1501d606a2ee0cdc0db9c7db1c571e504","tid":1010681,"uid":222165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T09:33:45.000Z","msg":"WTF<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全民愛滋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f87a60c92335c0c8