" target=\"_blank\">https://www.canada.ca/en/public-health/services/laboratory-biosafety-biosecurity/pathogen-safety-data-sheets-risk-assessment/human-immunodeficiency-virus.html</a><br />\n或者升少少溫度都ok"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T10:23:50.000Z","msg":"咁你上去打返支先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770afb789649cffcb6f445c50175d08751f5a6c3","tid":1010681,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T10:23:57.000Z","msg":"陳豪愛滋針.jpg"},{"pid":"c88fd7d96583cfd4a4f19d9d733730fbbe689dda","tid":1010681,"uid":134949,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T10:25:05.000Z","msg":"疫苗驗岀愛滋病抗體，中國或成最後大贏家！"},{"pid":"ef2555830b6b61528270f450190cfcd531734f58","tid":1010681,"uid":85805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T10:26:04.000Z","msg":"諗起病港"},{"pid":"cfe95d1ec72e069a17a00d91d9ba6d79524244c7","tid":1010681,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T10:26:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcR_28MoIZxPg6q_DnOKyNTn5ZnnNQSvnxNVFU8v1xrSJq2oulR_\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcR_28MoIZxPg6q_DnOKyNTn5ZnnNQSvnxNVFU8v1xrSJq2oulR_&h=2a635511&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b96808fd0a574e44aed925a9a68f1284c77ef41","tid":1010681,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T10:26:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JipHeST.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJipHeST.jpg&h=aaea7fe1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a6d39a8f98d883d7c726f6a7bcd3013d05324bd","tid":1010681,"uid":21052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T10:31:09.000Z","msg":"痴線 有咩事全世界一齊玩完<br />\n中國果然係癌細胞"},{"pid":"1c60b185d8b449c335f5b397d371cb7bafe4b8ce","tid":1010681,"uid":38030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT